sentence: A look at the weighted underlying holdings of the WisdomTree U.S. LargeCap Dividend Fund ( DLN ) shows an impressive 12.3% of holdings on a weighted basis have experienced insider buying within the past six months.

AT&T Inc (Symbol: T), which makes up 3.18% of the WisdomTree U.S. LargeCap Dividend Fund ( DLN ), has seen 9 directors and officers purchase shares in the past six months, according to the recent Form 4 data.
The ETF holds a total of $58,065,299 worth of T, making it the #1 largest holding.
